data.description: You are sure to love this tastefully updated 4 bedrooms, 1.5 bath home in the City of Hastings - walking distance from the schools. The main floor has a brand new kitchen - featuring solid surface countertops, new cabinets, SS appliances, & snack bar. The kitchen opens into the spacious living with recently added canned lights and fan. The main floor holds 3 nicely sized bedrooms, and 1 full bath. The walk out lower level expands the living space with a fourth bed, half bath - generous sized living area, laundry room, and dedicated storage space. Outside you'll find a fully fenced backyard, and back patio that looks over the 24' above ground pool. An added bonus is a hookup for a generator. Recently re-poured driveway, and new mulch in the landscape. Don't miss out on this home today!!
